♪Burning flames consume our past♪

286
00:18:07,136 --> 00:18:12,305
♪How to break these binding chains♪

287
00:18:12,896 --> 00:18:18,278
♪We decide our own fate♪

288
00:18:18,278 --> 00:18:23,938
♪Who should I ask to end this plight♪

289
00:18:23,938 --> 00:18:28,080
♪When cocoons break, we'll reunite♪

290
00:18:28,080 --> 00:18:31,880
Why did you come back?

291
00:18:34,480 --> 00:18:35,520
They all say

